# .claude.local.md — Machine-Specific Config
# Copy to .claude.local.md and customize for your machine.
# This file is gitignored — safe for local paths, ports, and overrides.

## Local Paths
# - Repo: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/Gits/brainlayer
# - Python venv: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/Gits/brainlayer/.venv
# - BrainLayer DB: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/Library/Application Support/BrainBar/brainlayer.db

## BrainBar Daemon
# - Socket: /tmp/brainbar.sock
# - App: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/Applications/BrainBar.app

## Enrichment Config
# - BRAINLAYER_ENRICH_BACKEND: mlx (default on Apple Silicon) or ollama
# - Auto-enrich on brain_store uses Gemini Flash Lite (separate from backend)
# - Gemini API key location: 1Password vault "development"

## Dev Flags
# - debug_mode: false
# - test_db_path: /tmp/brainlayer-test.db
